lings for his classmate Janu.","genre_ids":[10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9669,"vote_count":139,"poster_path":"/nrVloCa2hCFOztRF1DZU2jnWIiQ.jpg","release_date":"2018-10-04","vote_average":7.673,"backdrop_path":"/qzu94AvnZ1az30sTUuibx2bXpfs.jpg","original_title":"96","original_language":"ta"},{"id":937020,"adult":false,"title":"Jailer","video":false,"overview":"Muthuvel Pandian, a retired, stern yet compassionate jailer lives a peaceful life with his family, but trouble knocks his door when his cop son’s tryst with an antique mafia gang goes awry and forces Muthu to step back into a dark world he had voluntarily took a break from.","genre_ids":[28,80,53,35,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9757,"vote_count":105,"poster_path":"/pTmMxAHqX4vsIDE6HPPxOR0Q6TN.jpg","release_date":"2023-08-10","vote_average":6.624,"backdrop_path":"/ownDZBS9ecoPbWjW5V5L8jknGF.jpg","original_title":"ஜெயிலர்","original_language":"ta"},{"id":577328,"adult":false,"title":"Kabir Singh","video":false,"overview":"Kabir, a genius yet hostile medical student, falls in love with Preeti from his college. When Preeti's father spots the couple kissing, he opposes their relationship and decides to marry her off.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1025,"vote_count":174,"poster_path":"/unqiPjtc6CGqs13zho7ZvWU85zu.jpg","release_date":"2019-06-20","vote_average":6.342,"backdrop_path":"/yFwn006ETsYVykpI8OKocgY0Bi3.jpg","original_title":"कबीर सिंह","original_language":"hi"},{"id":282070,"adult":false,"title":"Parasyte: Part 2","video":false,"overview":"Humanity is under attack by human-mimicking flesh-eating alien parasites. One parasite bonds with his young high school student host, and he convinces the parasite to help him stop the others.","genre_ids":[878,27,28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1295,"vote_count":205,"poster_path":"/qO8zQ9dSADWiwRnR7oCOsPDuOom.jpg","release_date":"2015-04-25","vote_average":7.054,"backdrop_path":"/vT4bg2mKaJ3cPLxlwotuewC0LZk.