":"/qqsz34AfEAyaq3XWsfpxbY0gKak.jpg","original_title":"ソウル","original_language":"ja"},{"id":8452,"adult":false,"title":"The 6th Day","video":false,"overview":"A world of the very near future in which cattle, fish, and even the family pet can be cloned. But cloning humans is illegal - that is until family man Adam Gibson comes home from work one day to find a clone has replaced him. Taken from his family and plunged into a sinister world he doesn't understand, Gibson must not only save himself from the assassins who must destroy him to protect their secret, but uncover who and what is behind the horrible things happening to him.","genre_ids":[878,28,9648,18,53],"popularity":4.0681,"vote_count":2205,"poster_path":"/rODFJOFiPk1UVCe4pmBza8T6feO.jpg","release_date":"2000-11-17","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/opkt6IK1Os5gAwhlpu27bCZCk8K.jpg","original_title":"The 6th Day","original_language":"en"},{"id":8456,"adult":false,"title":"Never Back Down","video":false,"overview":"Jake, full of anger after his father's death, is just starting to find a place for himself at his new Orlando high school - until Ryan, head of an underground MMA fight club, picks Jake out as a prime opponent. After being trounced by Ryan in front of the entire school, Jake begins training under the firm, moral guidance of a MMA master, where he learns how to fight... and how to avoid a fight. But it becomes obvious that a rematch will be inevitable if Jake wants to stop Ryan and his bullying, once and for all.","genre_ids":[18,28],"popularity":4.4077,"vote_count":2442,"poster_path":"/8oRUTyP1QAtGDMvRpKZyuyFPG0U.jpg","release_date":"2008-03-04","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/h71xyiurUscD6uIPbECyso1Lwb9.jpg","original_title":"Never Back Down","original_language":"en"},{"id":277542,"adult":false,"title":"Perfect Lover","video":false,"overview":"In a futuristic world where women run the show, a shy plastics designer buys a female robot, so he gains confidence and becomes a ladies' man.","genre_ids":[878,35],"popularity":0.3005,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/gyrOXxrPL6i08UAjkDUbnV5hS3d.jpg","release_date":"2001-01-20","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Perfect Lover","original_language":"en"},{"id":8216,"adult":false,"title":"Meet the Feebles","video":false,"overview":"Heidi, star of the \"Meet The Feebles Variety Hour\" discovers her lover Bletch the Walrus is cheating on her. And with all the world waiting for the show, the assorted co-stars must contend with drug addiction, extortion, robbery, disease, drug dealing, and murder.","genre_ids":[35,10402,14],"popularity":1.2726,"vote_count":311,"poster_path":"/31DqGazwdE9N4Y9FHC6Q4NvstuW.jpg","release_date":"1989-08-12","vote_average":6.339,"backdrop_path":"/fji432Vjgj89p0ISOJONYyfNUmy.jpg","original_title":"Meet the Feebles","original_language":"en"},{"id":8292,"adult":false,"title":"Four Brothers","video":false,"overview":"Four adopted brothers return to their Detroit hometown when their mother is murdered and vow to exact revenge on the killers.","genre_ids":[28,80],"popularity":4.497,"vote_count":2328,"poster_path":"/8cO39cnWSZQi2ncPG5TxL3YRzKc.jpg","release_date":"2005-08-11","vote_average":6.805,"backdrop_path":"/2pITFeesu6aikrEknoH6bNXOdhk.jpg","original_title":"Four Brothers","original_language":"en"},{"id":8373,"adult":false,"title":"Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen","video":false,"overview":"Sam Witwicky leaves the Autobots behind for a normal life. But when his mind is filled with cryptic symbols, the Decepticons target him and he is dragged back into the Transformers' war.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":2.9923,"vote_count":9019,"poster_path":"/pLBb0whOzVDtJvyD4DPeQyQNOqp.jpg","release_date":"2009-06-19","vote_average":6.211,"backdrop_path":"/bH1bhjn37uA1zOPvyHbzJSvza7v.jpg","original_title":"Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen","original_language":"en"},{"id":8382,"adult":false,"title":"Today You Die","video":false,"overview":"A former thief who is trying to go straight seeks vengeance on those who framed him.","genre_ids":[28,80,12,53],"popularity":0.8781,"vote_count":121,"poster_path":"/fSL56vXRp4Qh23vXPiAhJMFKZgB.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-13","vote_average":4.3,"backdrop_path":"/9XpbzvX38LUi21QYvBlVyp3yBMv.jpg","original_title":"Today You Die","original_language":"en"},{"id":661709,"adult":false,"title":"Ghost of Machine","video":false,"overview":"An outdated babysitting robot becomes too obsessed with the family.","genre_ids":[27,878],"popularity":0.1854,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/9bS3xYWYgEAZkNx1dWcFhJprA6h.jpg","release_date":"2016-06-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/xK4iGtzpb7q28quvWMnRhYMHEBw.jpg","original_title":"기계령","original_language":"ko"},{"id":8840,"adult":false,"title":"DragonHeart","video":false,"overview":"In an ancient time when majestic fire-breathers soared through the skies, a knight named Bowen comes face to face and heart to heart with the last dragon on Earth, Draco. Taking up arms to suppress a tyrant king, Bowen soon realizes his task will be harder than he'd imagined: If he kills the king, Draco will die as well.","genre_ids":[14,28,12,18],"popularity":3.9928,"vote_count":2106,"poster_path":"/1J2FvxEoEKMFT9TjUdfhm0MJhZD.jpg","release_date":"1996-05-31","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/xbqluNfftDJtxDsqcpx9kKme4LF.jpg","original_title":"DragonHeart","original_language":"en"},{"id":661996,"adult":false,"title":"Un Hombre Violento","video":false,"overview":"Bent on avenging the death of his gambling addicted father, Julian Carrera embarks on a violent spree with deadly consequences.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"popularity":0.1996,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/wOw0EtETlLyqcDG1Xq3GtaZWj3F.jpg","release_date":"1984-01-01","vote_average":4.2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Un Hombre Violento","original_language":"es"},{"id":8851,"adult":false,"title":"The Blob","video":false,"overview":"A drive-in favorite, this sci-fi classic follows teenagers Steve and his best girl, Jane, as they try to protect their hometown from a gelatinous alien life form that engulfs everything it touches. The first to discover the substance and live to tell about it, Steve and Jane witness the blob destroying an elderly man, then it growing to a terrifying size. But no one else has seen the goo, and policeman Dave refuses to believe the kids without proof.","genre_ids":[27,878],"popularity":2.2651,"vote_count":645,"poster_path":"/ctOwn1Ibg3SjDG4WulvFvSH0PRT.jpg","release_date":"1958-09-10","vote_average":6.216,"backdrop_path":"/32l2szM3oY7kdI3TMBral5dsc2E.jpg","original_title":"The Blob","original_language":"en"},{"id":8856,"adult":false,"title":"The Karate Kid Part II","video":false,"overview":"Summoned by his dying father, Miyagi returns to his homeland of Okinawa, with Daniel, after a 40-year exile. There he must confront Yukie, the love of his youth, and Sato, his former best friend turned vengeful rival. Sato is bent on a fight to the death, even if it means the destruction of their village. Daniel finds his own love in Yukia's niece, Kumiko, and his own enemy in Sato's nephew, the vicious Chozen. Now, far away from the tournaments, cheering crowds and safety of home, Daniel will face his greatest challenge ever when the cost of honor is life itself.","genre_ids":[12,18,28,10749,10751],"popularity":3.5398,"vote_count":2415,"poster_path":"/k0OwgRR6PNu7h3SiqpCbRdZWNaG.jpg","release_date":"1986-06-18","vote_average":6.335,"backdrop_path":"/7rfcRXbFD0xr8NteNq1hwXUd4Af.jpg","original_title":"The Karate Kid Part II","original_language":"en"},{"id":8860,"adult":false,"title":"Metro","video":false,"overview":"Roper, a hostage negotiator catches a murderous bank robber after a blown heist. The bank robber escapes and immediately goes after the man who put him behind bars.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"popularity":1.3449,"vote_count":601,"poster_path":"/nvfyHYv1EDpYai5pCGqBeRf3tax.jpg","release_date":"1997-01-16","vote_average":5.704,"backdrop_path":"/vGzPiKNj3Tw9NR4F6EyexqniEqm.jpg","original_title":"Metro","original_language":"en"},{"id":8867,"adult":false,"title":"The Punisher","video":false,"overview":"The avenging angel of Marvel Comics fame comes brilliantly to life in this searing action-adventure thriller! Dolph Lundgren stars as Frank Castle, a veteran cop who loses his entire family to a mafia car bomb. His ex-partner believes Castle survived the blast and became the Punisher, living in the sewers and exacting vigilante violence against mob bosses throughout the city. When the populace is caught in the midst of a gang war that he caused, Castle must again emerge from the shadows and save the innocent.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"popularity":2.1304,"vote_count":653,"poster_path":"/tA0O0hYyHX7Hl2Fl8VEtGtfBtjI.jpg","release_date":"1989-10-05","vote_average":5.768,"backdrop_path":"/tFmrdnfXM0p6ihMTFpptYOKEfSl.jpg","original_title":"The Punisher","original_language":"en"},{"id":8870,"adult":false,"title":"Red Planet","video":false,"overview":"Astronauts search for solutions to save a dying Earth by searching on Mars, only to have the mission go terribly awry.","genre_ids":[53,28,878],"popularity":3.2561,"vote_count":1128,"poster_path":"/6svTVlVEJDoOOEz1G09HLeb7vtF.jpg","release_date":"2000-11-10","vote_average":5.719,"backdrop_path":"/zZcqSA3vudSPSLHjsvfnGJQpOKe.jpg","original_title":"Red Planet","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt5080556","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q21095433","instagram_id":null,"rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/20_2018"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148537,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AU","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2018-11-29T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"M"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CA","